{
  "stem": "14613.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I don't remember exactly, but I think about six, seven years-- when I was six, seven years old.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I mentioned before, I went together with all my siblings to the Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jewish gymnasium was set up in such a way that they were separate schools for, for boys and separate schools for the girls.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that there was a separation between the sexes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I started at about six, seven years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was really a very fine school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The, the, the teachers in Poland were, by and large, scholars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they really knew the subject.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they knew how to teach.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And ours-- our work-- really, schoolwork, was divided into two halves, what I can call.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "About half of the day, we studied everything in Polish, whether it was Polish language and geometry, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] mathematics, or history.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was all in Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then, we also had an additional load, which did not exist in elementary school, in Polish school, or public school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we, we studied Hebrew, which also included the history, Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It included, also, the study of Torah, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In our home, we, as children, did not speak Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We spoke Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, of course, since we studied Hebrew, we, we, we understood, and we could speak Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But really, we did not speak Hebrew at home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My parents spoke to us in Polish, except when they did not want us to understand something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then they either spoke to themselves Russian or sometimes Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The composition of-- oh, you're asking me questions which I already forgot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Remember, that's not only before the war-- that's way, way before the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
